          "is_optional": false,
          "note": null,
          "quantity_kind": "unquantified",
          "raw_text": "Heat a large nonstick skillet over medium-high heat. Add oil to pan; swirl to coat. Add corn and next 3 ingredients (through pepper) to pan; saut\u00e9 2 minutes. Add potatoes and tomatoes to pan; cook 1 minute. Top with cilantro and cheese."
        },
        {
          "ingredient_id": "d258ecd5-0009-4b49-8731-e29068058a0e",
          "input_qty": null,
          "input_unit_id": null,
          "is_optional": false,
          "note": null,
